  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to promote a prevention of the complications using an elaborate
      guide effective and easy to understand.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The puerperium consists the period of pregnancy and postpartum cycle that the alterations
      provoked for pregnancy and delivery on the women organism return to your state before
      pregnancy. The physiotherapist can follow the puerperium since hospital phase until women has
      been recovered of pregnancy physiologist alterations.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
